### LaTeX结构要求
```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{% raw %}{{% endraw %}{{ target_venue }}_style}  % 会议样式
\usepackage{graphicx}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{booktabs}

\begin{document}
\maketitle
\begin{abstract}...\end{abstract}
\section{Introduction}
\section{Related Work}
\section{Method}
\section{Experiments}
\section{Conclusion}
\bibliographystyle{plain}
\bibliography{related_work}
\end{document}
```

